name: Super Image Series #015
description:
Images from this series have been made using AI algorithms. The concept is to take a photo and downsizing it to a ridicoulously small resolution until it's just a mush of pixels; then upscale it using a 'super resolution' algorithm for the AI find details, colors and textures, this process is repeated 8 times.
medium : png image
resolution : 4096 x 4096 px
